**Core Infrastructure:**
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/acceptance-test-kit.ts`

**Domain Test Kits:**
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/coding-agent-orchestrator/orchestrator-test-kit.ts`
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/coding-session/coding-session-test-kit.ts`
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/intent-node/intent-test-kit.ts`
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/oauth-rar-dpop/oauth-test-kit.ts`
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/orchestrator-ui/orchestrator-ui-test-kit.ts`

**Example Tests Referenced:**
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/chat/phase1.test.ts` (basic chat smoke test)
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/extraction/pipeline.test.ts` (extraction + chat agent patterns)
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/intent-node/walking-skeleton.test.ts` (intent authorization E2E)
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/auth/oauth-mcp-auth.test.ts` (DPoP/MCP authentication)
- `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/hamburg/tests/acceptance/coding-session/walking-skeleton.test.ts` (agent orchestration + SSE)
