## 7. Test Infrastructure Features

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|-----------------|
| **Concurrent Uniqueness** | `crypto.randomUUID()` for IDs (never Date.now() alone) |
| **Inflight Work** | `deps.inflight.track(promise)` + `.drain()` in afterAll |
| **SSE Stream Parsing** | Manual `TextDecoder` + `split("\n\n")` + JSON.parse |
| **Schema SCHEMAFULL** | All tables strictly typed; nesting requires explicit field definitions |
| **RecordId Usage** | Cast directly as `as` (not wrapper functions); `.table.name` for table name |
| **Timeout Handling** | `withTimeout(callback, ms, label)` wraps Promise.race |
| **Test Data Isolation** | Each suite gets unique namespace/database; removed in afterAll |
| **Error Messages** | Full response bodies logged on fetch failures |
| **Mock Agent Support** | `ORCHESTRATOR_MOCK_AGENT=true` env var for testing orchestration logic |

